{"tid":772321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男警涉從警署證物偷86萬元現金　被告還柙候訊","createTime":"2018-08-08T16:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T02:02:35.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6c95d3efee2342aa3d20a0be1e7ce0d9c8b1fdc4","tid":772321,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"早前被發現在警察宿舍燒炭企圖自殺的一名警員，被揭疑在警署內監守自盜偷取86萬元現金證物，被控以盜竊罪名，案件今在粉嶺法院提堂，裁判官把案押後至10月3日再提訊，被告期間須還柙。<br />\n<br />\n被告劉永輝，41歲，被控於今年1至3月期間，在打鼓嶺警署地下G3室，偷取，當中包括678,545.5人民幣、34,964.9港元及8元美金，總值約86.5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n控方透露證物上驗出疑為被告指紋，稱需時索取法律意見，裁判官遂把案押後至10月3日再訊。被告並無申請保釋。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：FLCC2551/2018"},{"pid":"9556297f57d3643d9c52be8642d6f49730fa0810","tid":772321,"uid":192263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:57:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4a7ba040b9408e9502ab76b218c826af22f9d73","tid":772321,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:58:27.000Z","msg":"警方發言人又要重申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ad419140206bf029a22fafea66ed32e88ac30c","tid":772321,"uid":23162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:29:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撐警大聯盟又要出動，屌班物主老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></span>"},{"pid":"38bf7caef496e9a7d7abdd0b47accc152c7701ac","tid":772321,"uid":190928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:30:17.000Z","msg":"當更警加一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac53b0348848c228721ea2676e9767acc487307","tid":7